    public class SavedController

        Parameters:
        gameId - is the game id
        roundNumber - is the round number
        frenzy - is true if frenzy is active
        hasSomeoneDied - is true if someone in this turn died
        shotPlayerThisTurn - is a list of int of player that have been shot
        turnPhase - is the phase of the turn
        frenzyStarter - is the last player to play
        playerSize - is the number of players
        gameEnded - is true if the current one is the last round
